{"tid":2056653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：連登仔高質動畫籲天下圍中 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-09T00:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T01:45:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9af70ff59ce36287fafc6c8c28106212e03b5d64","tid":2056653,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200609/QS545PYEY7QZZDKIWA46FGO5CY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FQS545PYEY7QZZDKIWA46FGO5CY%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19phbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=4ad5f70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200609%2FQS545PYEY7QZZDKIWA46FGO5CY%2F&h=7036aa28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200609/QS545PYEY7QZZDKIWA46FGO5CY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：連登仔高質動畫籲天下圍中 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZFTGVQBDHXWMZA6ITXNCOREQKU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZFTGVQBDHXWMZA6ITXNCOREQKU.gif&h=e9eae68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月9日，對所有港人嚟講都係意義深遠嘅一日，除咗因百萬人上街，亦係抗爭運動開端。一年過去，全球俾武肺攻陷，北京趁全球分身不暇，全力喺香港推國安惡法。港人近排俾無力感包圍，不過好多手足仍默默抗爭。有連登巴打噚日上載一段高質抗爭動畫（圖），為手足們放上Twitter，仲好貼心咁整埋英文同普通話版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三種語言 上載Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條片全名係「香港國安法：對全球作出的最後呼喊」，影片製作手足喺連登貼文話：「希望用呢段抗爭動畫為香港喺咁困難嘅時間出一分力」。手足覺得各國反應可令反共陣<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n可以幫手喺Twitter上轉發呼籲各國齊心反共，connect更多唔同國家嘅人對準中共政權。<br />\n<br />\n條片真係十分高質，第一句就講中好多港人心聲，「2020，香港歷史上最黑暗的一年」，2019抗爭歲月好多令人揪心嘅畫面，一一再呈現眼前。畫面一轉，就係一個習<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n黑手爪向地球，「昨日新疆、今日香港，明日爪牙將蔓延至世界」，港人身影，就成為咗抗極權最前線，呼籲世界同港人線成一線。手足最後<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n集，希望有機會再出片。八方唯一挑剔嘅地方，就係點解得三種語言，各位繙譯師快啲幫吓手！"},{"pid":"51ae26c7b9978c3f0ef8cefb6bf560d15114a09a","tid":2056653,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"【突發】全力推上國際！攬炒團隊 《時代革命一周年動畫》 6/9正式上線！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2056637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2056637</a>"},{"pid":"cbfedc06db343a7b80aba2138e73732c21a2fe83","tid":2056653,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05cf1bdaeab72791a4331c287592575cca60fe26","tid":2056653,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40d56a352f073152b8c09c6080641f93d5874b4","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:42:42.000Z","msg":"屌 柏金遜發作 hi左個負皮sor <br />\n自罰推10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2623ad242a1edbc4da3164f951a2666582b222e2","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"bcae50e04a0989eee11484d5b7bcfec892bf1bf5","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"512c36036ef2637f4365bd356a3db181df1c3cb7","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"986f2494bee81b0bae35180dbf11bc968b5f769f","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"fb6fe8f8c0b7369bd62f8ddcc090d4c86da42495","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"ba883f8d963675387de5fa39600b0fe68f07e0e3","tid":2056653,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"a58a49d4864ef9d20e1231782c5b50a25aca9ec1","tid":2